name: Confused#012
description:
@M_lon - These series of avatars are inspired by my journey through the NFTs world. It is amazing drawing someone’s face, sometimes without even meeting that person before, allowing me to dream and imagine new worlds while making art.

Chromatic Aberration as a technique, comes from my relationship with presbyopia, and with it, I invite you to see through my eyes (when I’m not wearing glasses).
